,Recommended,251170,8502916,"Posted: 2 January, 2014",all,PAL-18 🐢,"This game is very very fun.  And gameplay is simple yet very complex.There are 4 humans trying to escape a building.  Throughout each map are keys and other items that the humans need to find in order to escape.  The placement of the items and paths randomize on each map so you have a different experience each time.  As a human you use a combination of left mouse button and mouse movements to open and close doors and drawers.  You also get a flashlight and you can sprint for short periods of time (with a slow regen of sprint).  You can't fight the monsters; all you can do is run, hide and die.There are 2 types of monsters with very different abilities.  The basic mission for the monster is to kill all the humans which is often easier said than done.This game is very fun to play as people will regularly freak out and scream sounding like a little girl.  GET IT NOW!"
